@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Reports";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="about-content">
    <p>
        Welcome to the Reports section! This is where you can generate detailed reports on your expenses and income over specific periods.
        Our reporting tools are designed to give you a comprehensive view of your financial activities, helping you to make informed decisions.
    </p>

    <h2>Why Reports Matter</h2>
    <p>
        Generating reports is crucial for understanding your financial health and making strategic decisions about your budgeting and spending.
        Regularly reviewing your reports enables you to identify trends, pinpoint areas for improvement, and set realistic financial goals.
    </p>

    <h2>Key Features of Our Reporting Tool</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Generate monthly, quarterly, and yearly summaries to gain insights into your financial health. These summaries provide a clear overview of your income and expenses over time.</li>
        <li>Review categorized breakdowns of your spending habits and trends. Understanding where your money goes allows you to adjust your budgeting strategies effectively.</li>
        <li>Use reports to make more informed decisions about budgeting and saving. With accurate data at your fingertips, you can create more effective financial plans.</li>
        <li>Export your reports as PDFs or other formats for further analysis. This feature allows you to share your financial information easily with advisors or family members.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Generating Reports</h2>
    <p>
        Our reporting system provides various options to cater to your needs. Here’s how you can make the most of it:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Creating Different Types of Reports:</strong> Generate a variety of reports, including monthly summaries, category-wise spending, and trend analyses. This flexibility ensures you get the insights that matter most to you.</li>
        <li><strong>Visual Data Representation:</strong> Utilize charts and graphics that make understanding your data easier. Visual aids enhance comprehension and allow for quicker insights into your financial patterns.</li>
        <li><strong>Customizable Reporting Periods:</strong> Choose specific date ranges for your reports, allowing you to analyze your financial performance over timeframes that are significant to you.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Start Generating Reports Today!</h2>
    <p>
        Take advantage of our reporting features to gain a deeper understanding of your finances.
        With the ability to generate detailed reports, you will be better equipped to track your progress and make informed financial decisions.
    </p>
</div>
